      "content" : "<!-- dialog -->\n<dialog data-template=\"Dialog\">\n  <img src=\"\/assets\/images\/cookie-monster.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"An excited purple cookie monster with his hands raised asking please.\" width=\"284\" height=\"180\" \/>\n  <h1>Could I <em>please<\/em> have a few small cookies?<\/h1>\n  <p>I <em>really hate<\/em> to ask, but cookies help me to understand why folks like you are visiting my site, where they are from, and how I can look to improve my site for everyone in the future.<\/p>\n  <hr class=\"dotted\">\n  <form method=\"dialog\">\n\t<button title=\"No way! (Unfortunately do I need a cookie to remind myself not to bother you about cookies anymore.) #irony\" type=\"cancel\"><span>NO WAY!<\/span><\/button>\n\t<button title=\"Okay\" type=\"submit\"><span>OKAY!<\/span><\/button>\n  <\/form>\n<\/dialog>",
